      • getWaitFactorMultiplier

        public int getWaitFactorMultiplier(AlertDefinition definition)
        Gets the wait factor multiplier off of the definition, returning INTERVAL_WAIT_FACTOR_DEFAULT if not specified. This will look for STALE_INTERVAL_MULTIPLIER_PARAM_KEY in the definition parameters. The value returned from this method will be guaranteed to be in the range of 2 to 10.
        Parameters:
        definition - the definition to read
        Returns:
        the wait factor interval multiplier
